[Middle school students poisoning incident in Shanghai]
According to media reports, on September 12, several students in a middle school on Xia Nan Road, Pudong, Shanghai, felt unwell.
After investigation, it was found that two students added a mixed liquid with cleaning and bleaching effects into their classmates' water cups during physical education class that morning, causing several students to feel unwell.
